data.description: Beautiful colonial style two story home in sought-after, Secluded Hills subdivision located in the school Don Robert’s zone. This incredible property features a beautifully updated kitchen, hardwoods on main level and spacious bedrooms! Downstairs presents a cozy marble fireplace, and two extra rooms, not accounted for in the bedrooms that can be used as an office, study or play area.
